            .about-left
                .about-left__pic
                    img.about-left__img(src="assets/images/portrait.jpg", alt="In Young Choi")
            .about-right
                h2.about-right__title About Me.
                .about-right__subtitle Frontend Developer
                .about-right__desc
                    p My name is #[b In Young Choi]. I love coding and developing user-friendly websites. I make Static, Liquid, Adaptive, or Responsive sites, code sites PSD to HTML & CSS. 
                    p I am interested in doing quality work on the conscience and making it nice for you and me. I’m responsible and well organised. 
                    p I like to learn and develop in technology. Not afraid of hard work. I will do my best to work with you. I am always looking for new modern solutions, creative approach, help with advice and offer options for profitable conditions.
                .skills
                    .skillbar.clearfix(data-percent='95%')
