                        .skillbar-bar(style='background: #2ecc71;')
                        .skill-bar-percent 70%
                    // End Skill Bar
        section.services#services
            h2.about-right__title.services__title Services.
            .services-block
                ul.services__list
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-desktop
                        h5.services__item-title Web development
                        p.services__item-desk I develop custom websites, keeping them unique, functional and modern. Considering the latest technologies like HTML5, CSS3, PHP and more.
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-id-card-o
                        h5.services__item-title Design logos and corporate identity
                        p.services__item-desk When a company begins to consider ways to visually represent themselves, their product, service. Together with you I make an appealing design that suits your business.
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-window-maximize 
                        h5.services__item-title Adaptive development
                        p.services__item-desk A website must be properly viewed on a wide variety of screens. I make sure that your website is always optimally usable on any device.
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-lock 
                        h5.services__item-title Maintenance & Support
                        p.services__item-desk I provide on-going support and maintenance services to ensure that your website always runs smoothly. I provide honest advice and the best possible support for you to reach your goals.
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-file-code-o 
                        h5.services__item-title Website restyling
                        p.services__item-desk I can help you to update it into a modern, user-friendly and responsive website that will convert more visitors into customers and boost your conversion rate.
                    li.services__item 
                        .services__item-block
                            .services__item-icon
                                i.fa.fa-line-chart 
                        h5.services__item-title SEO
                        p.services__item-desk Regardless if you already work, live and breathe the internet or if you’re just about to craft your online presence, there’s one magic term that you’ve probably heard of – SEO. I can help improve the visibility of a website in search engines. The primary function of SEO is to drive more useful traffic to a site that converts into sales.
        section.portfolio#portfolio
            h2.about-right__title.services__title.portfolio__title Portfolio.
